The paper deals with a scheduling problem in manufacturing, logistics, and project management, which is a common topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method involves decision rules and local search, which are also common techniques in data structures (cs.DS) and optimization (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the properties of execution strategies, which can be considered a machine learning problem (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with uncertainty and robustness, which are common topics in control systems (cs.SY).
